The street below is lit up with lights, and there are people walking along the sidewalks. The balcony has a simple metal railing and matching chairs.
The image shows a man standing in a formal garden in Italy. The garden features manicured hedges, tall cypress trees, and statues. The caption includes the hashtag "#mangiare" (Italian for "to eat").

The image shows a road leading towards a mountain range, likely the High Tatras, as indicated by the hashtags. It appears to be a rural or scenic area.
The image is a close-up shot of a brown terrier-type dog. The caption refers to the dog as "Maxa a.k.a. The Yoda dog."

The image shows a scenic view of a town or city nestled in a valley, with mountains in the background and a vibrant, colorful sunset or sunrise sky. The foreground features trees and a field. The location is identified as Roznava in the post.
